  "description": "Machine-readable mapping of Section 2 artifact names to their parent record types, discriminator fields (JSON Pointer), and discriminator values. Enables template authors to use exists_where rules with well-known discriminator paths, and SDK implementations to validate that variant names in templates resolve to real record types and payload fields.",
